{"about_the_game":"After waking up in a strange device with no idea how you got there you must find your way through a twisted but breathtaking world littered<br>with artifacts of past destruction.<br><br>Create your own custom character with our comprehensive character creator.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/extras/TheWayGIF01.gif?t=1712763690\" /><br><br>And take on the world, find out where you are and what is going on.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/extras/TheWayGIF02.gif?t=1712763690\" />  <br><br>But be careful and watch your step. This world can be dangerous and slippery with it's physics based damage and enemy interactions. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/extras/TheWayGIF03.gif?t=1712763690\" /><br><br>And remember you can always rest anywhere and have some fun while your health recovers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/extras/TheWayGIF04.gif?t=1712763690\" /> <br><br>&quot;The Way&quot; is a third or first person physics based real-time action exploration game with character customization and role-playing but very different<br>from the established D&amp;D RPG formula making it hard to fit in any established genre. It is ADULTS ONLY game for it contains nudity, violence <br>and sex but they are not central to the game. The main focus of the game is realistic exploring and finding your way through the strange world. The game is designed to provide real life like feel of the world both with it's control system as well as with it's realistic graphics.<br><br>Features:<br>-Unique highly detailed world with rich history.<br>-Comprehensive character creator.<br>-Realistic movement system. <br>-Physics based damage system. <br>-Intriguing story.<br>-Navigation puzzles.<br>-Graphics that push Unity HDRP to it's limits.<br><br>As our game is still in development expect some bugs and unfinished features.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1712763690","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1712763690","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1712763690","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1712763690","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,3,4,5],"notes":"The Way contains full frontal nudity for both sexes and animated sex."},"demos":[{"appid":2518800,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"After waking up in a strange device with no idea how you got there you must find your way through a twisted but breathtaking world littered<br>with artifacts of past destruction.<br><br>Create your own custom character with our comprehensive character creator.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/extras/TheWayGIF01.gif?t=1712763690\" /><br><br>And take on the world, find out where you are and what is going on.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/extras/TheWayGIF02.gif?t=1712763690\" />  <br><br>But be careful and watch your step. This world can be dangerous and slippery with it's physics based damage and enemy interactions. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495780/extras/TheWayGIF03.gif?t=1712763690\" /><br><br>And remember you can always rest anywhere and have some fun while your health recovers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co